{"tid":845573,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"傷害完人真係會有報應","createTime":"2018-10-02T18:47:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T20:25:52.000Z","uid":41773,"like":26,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"aee1cae2ae022e729f155e32bb2da8af1341186a","tid":845573,"uid":41773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T18:47:12.000Z","msg":"傷害得ex太深，到依家分左手十個月都仲未走得返出黎<br />\n每日都會因為自己做錯既事而頹，晚晚都仲會發惡夢<br />\n然後係人地面前仲要扮到無野呀過得好好咁樣<br />\n<br />\n雖然我知道呢啲真係因果報應，但到底要捱到幾時<br />\n我真係辛苦到就黎死，又唔敢搵人講，係咪真係要一世無了期咁樣過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25b375d38cd6ce8b35074922a241fbb059d02447","tid":845573,"uid":41773,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T18:56:28.000Z","msg":"所以有時講野做野真係要諗過先做<br />\n如果唔係傷害到人個種內疚感真係可以折磨死你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a975f3d6f6eb41d7b5ab68ee25940e5f88b86039","tid":845573,"uid":431,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T18:59:34.000Z","msg":"仆街係唔抵可憐"},{"pid":"c5d7659a913f9bd108124937f4b58634e655edf2","tid":845573,"uid":41773,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a975f3d6f6eb41d7b5ab68ee25940e5f88b86039","tid":845573,"uid":431,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T18:59:34.000Z","msg":"仆街係唔抵可憐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T19:00:27.000Z","msg":"絕對同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a886b046707cf46820b8174cdb768e3a0c0cdcb","tid":845573,"uid":16425,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T19:22:27.000Z","msg":"岩吵 分手係自己講嫁 到人地封哂你喇 先發覺仲好在意<br />\n無啦 係自己講嫁 無都得後悔 真係報應黎<br />\n可惜沒如果呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hk